# qweret MARKET - STOCKS DASHBOARD

A Flask web app that tracks Top 500 stocks via Yahoo Finance with BUY/HOLD/SELL signals.

## Features
- Dashboard — Top 10 scored stocks as highlight cards with sparklines
- All Stocks — Full table (desktop) / card list (mobile) with search, filter, sort
- Stock Detail — Price history chart, previous/current/predicted prices, full stats, investment signal breakdown
- Responsive: table on desktop, cards on mobile 

## Setup

bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run the app
python app.py


Then open http://localhost:5000

## How Scoring Works

| Factor | Points |
|--------|--------|
| RSI < 30 (Oversold) | +20 |
| RSI > 70 (Overbought) | -20 |
| Strong Uptrend | +30 |
| Uptrend | +15 |
| Strong Downtrend | -30 |
| Downtrend | -15 |
| Daily change > 2% | +20 |
| Daily change > 0% | +10 |
| Daily change < -2% | -20 |
| Daily change < 0% | -10 |

Score 70–100 = BUY | Score 40–69 = HOLD | Score 0–39 = SELL


> ⚠️ Not financial advice. For informational/educational use only.
